cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for recognizing human body poses across multiple views. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach for learning a compact view-invariant embedding space, which involves probabilistic embeddings and deep learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with analyzing body movements and human behaviors in images and videos, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.RO (Robotics).
